This is a demonstration for the usage of https://github.com/tfrancoi/odoo_csv_import and https://github.com/tfrancoi/easier_import

Installation
============
1) Create an odoo 11 database named "load" with sale_management, import_metadata, import_res_id and purchase installed
2) Create users with name and login Thibault and Francois
3) activate the following lang French (BE) / Fran√ßais (BE), English, Dutch / Nederlands

Your are good to go

Test
====
 
sh transform.sh
sh load.sh

You've all your data into your database
